name: 1.68somerville1
body:
dell-recovery (1.68somerville1) jammy; urgency=medium

  [ chris ]
  * DHC: DHC+Ubuntu pop dialog with Nvidia Card Invisble the option Recovery DHC Hybird Client when launch Dell Recovery tool

  [ Shih-Yuan Lee (FourDollars) ]
  * collections.Callable is removed since Python 3.10.
  * Preseed values for ubiquity/download_updates and ubiquity/use_nonfree to skip some page during the installation.
  * Support the zstd compression format.
  * Follow cd-boot-images-amd64/xorriso-cmd.txt to build the ISO image.

 -- Shih-Yuan Lee (FourDollars) <sylee@canonical.com>  Sat, 19 Mar 2022 23:24:21 +0800

New logging capabilities
Updates for bugs found
Turn off secure boot Mok stuff by default
